caller_intent: Adina Salajin wanted to discuss her insurance policy renewal and clarify details about the renewal cost, referencing a previous payment amount.
resolution_steps: Agent requested Adina's policy number and confirmed her name.
Agent accessed the account system to retrieve policy details.
Agent attempted to transfer Adina to the appropriate department for further assistance.
summary: Adina contacted Alliance Insurance regarding her policy renewal and a question about the renewal cost. The agent gathered her policy details and initiated a transfer to the appropriate department, but the call ended before resolution.
